content.html: Trans women are women. Gender is the child of misogyny. Demanding conforming to cis binary genders upholds the status quo patriarchy. If you exclude any marginalized genders in your advocacy, you're not a feminist. Consent culture is not just about sex. #WomensHistoryMonth
content.value:
Trans women are women.

Gender is the child of misogyny.

Demanding conforming to cis binary genders upholds the status quo patriarchy.

If you exclude any marginalized genders in your advocacy, you're not a feminist.

Consent culture is not just about sex. 

#WomensHistoryMonth
